}

\value{
  \code{chunkGrid} returns NULL or an \link{ArrayGrid} object defining a
  grid on reference array \code{x}.

  \code{chunkdim} returns NULL or the chunk dimensions in an integer vector
  parallel to \code{dim(x)}.
}

